@devtels: And, genius? Find the answer yourself? :)
You have to upload the "bin"- tree to your server and to type: www.yourserver/admin, thats all, tell me, if you see something now? :)
By that way: Great THX to ToXinax!

And: If you extract with winzip you poss. will get "error" on the end with question for replacing some 0-kb-files. Don't worry, you have to answer "Yes to all" or "Replace them all" or something, no problem it will be working fine.
